verse.lines:
{lang-eng}"Forever with the Lord!" Amen, so let it be;
Life from the dead is in that word,
'Tis immortality.
Here in the body pent, absent from Him I roam,
Yet nightly pitch my moving tent
A day's march nearer home.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}"Forever with the Lord!"
Father, if 'tis Thy will,
The promise of that faithful word
E'en here to me fulfill.
Be Thou at my right hand,
Then I can never fail;
Uphold Thou me, and I shall stand;
Fight, and I must prevail.{/lang-eng}
